# =============================================================================
# Large data files — not committed. The README documents how to source
# the raw dataset and regenerate data/processed/ and database/ecommerce.db
# by running the notebooks in order. Charts in visuals/ and the notebooks'
# own saved outputs are still versioned so reviewers can browse results
# without re-running anything.
# =============================================================================
data/raw/*.csv
data/processed/*.csv
database/*.db
# visuals/*.png

# =============================================================================
# Miscellaneous
# =============================================================================
*.log
*.tmp
.cache/
